These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, marigold
2 different pets are kept: fish, lizard
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person who growsorchid is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Flower        | orchid   | marigold   |
| Pet   | lizard | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, snake
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, old-henry
1. the dannemann-smoker is not to the left of the owner of the snake##8
2. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Pet   | snake | rabbit   |
| Cigar      | old-henry | dannemann |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, montecristo
2 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon
1. the baccarat-smoker is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Cigar          | montecristo | baccarat |
| Game   | monopoly   | backgammon     |

